{"tid":2439094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒爆福原愛「再也不回台灣」 江宏傑傳求解釋遭拒絕","createTime":"2021-03-09T03:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T11:45:52.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ca930ca6174b0b21dd0c0983fae13371d1bf49e8","tid":2439094,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"福原愛、江宏傑日前爆出婚變，但相隔一天雙方便發出聲明，否認外遇，也沒有離婚，不過日媒「女性自身」爆料指出，福原愛自從外遇緋聞，江宏傑希望她立刻回台灣解釋，卻被她拒絕，更爆料福原愛做出「再也不回台灣」的覺悟希望協議離婚，即便爆發緋聞之後，外界眼光對她不利，她離婚之心依舊強烈。<br />\n <br />\n「女性自身」引述認識他們夫妻的熟人表示，「江宏傑目前感到憤慨且難以置信，希望小愛趕快回台灣解釋，甚至提出可以去日本找小愛，卻都被小愛拒絕，看來夫妻關係是難以回復了」。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10088/5304467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Fstory%2F10088%2F5304467&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=7b090204\" target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10088/5304467</a>"},{"pid":"b36733a6bb5fcfab96d2ab9a7bc19dc86d35dbcb","tid":2439094,"uid":4574,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"媽的 廠商又有新題材"},{"pid":"5638d9bf141724511bff13fa1e63aa4004254671","tid":2439094,"uid":20867,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"消息指 福原愛 出軌勾佬前曾到過新北。。。"},{"pid":"fed41e4f8d1e375b279665428410a88696581f07","tid":2439094,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"NTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce164e0b8c69e6a3733c0ad8c2f197fd93325640","tid":2439094,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"仔女 同老母都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d99467e40656ce21e6534ae4e8ef86a6b56749e","tid":2439094,"uid":277992,"like":8,"dislike":0,